Adverse Drug Reaction/Event Report Form]

578
00:35:14,900 --> 00:35:18,540
[Huaren Medical University
Affiliated Hospital, Inpatient Record]

579
00:35:23,780 --> 00:35:29,340
[136 Zhang He Email Inbox]
[Gu Yunzheng]

580
00:35:29,340 --> 00:35:30,540
[Delete]

581
00:35:37,380 --> 00:35:38,220
This won't do.

582
00:35:38,340 --> 00:35:39,140
Okay.

583
00:35:39,140 --> 00:35:39,900
Su Wei'an,

584
00:35:40,820 --> 00:35:42,020
why are you here only now?

585
00:35:42,380 --> 00:35:43,660
Are you feeling unwell?

586
00:35:44,020 --> 00:35:44,820
No.

587
00:35:45,380 --> 00:35:46,660
I was handling some personal things.

588
00:35:48,380 --> 00:35:50,060
Handling personal things
during work hours?

589
00:35:50,380 --> 00:35:52,260
This is absenteeism.

590
00:35:54,900 --> 00:35:56,020
Look at the time now.

591
00:35:58,700 --> 00:35:59,820
The files I delivered to Prof. Wen

592
00:35:59,820 --> 00:36:01,140
were blocked by Wen Ran.

593
00:36:01,140 --> 00:36:02,900
I went to Zhang He Hospital this morning

594
00:36:02,900 --> 00:36:04,260
to resubmit them.

595
00:36:06,820 --> 00:36:08,380
Go ahead if you want to fine me.

596
00:36:08,380 --> 00:36:09,780
It's your lab after all.

597
00:36:15,460 --> 00:36:17,260
You could've told me that earlier.

598
00:36:17,580 --> 00:36:19,580
It's not like I'll do it every time.

599
00:36:23,900 --> 00:36:24,900
You know what.

600
00:36:24,900 --> 00:36:26,380
Zhang He Hospital

601
00:36:26,580 --> 00:36:28,260
is known for its low efficiency.

602
00:36:28,660 --> 00:36:29,380
I sent an email

603
00:36:29,380 --> 00:36:31,220
to their public mailbox last weekend.

604
00:36:31,340 --> 00:36:32,900
But there's no reply even now.

605
00:36:34,900 --> 00:36:36,060
That's odd.

606
00:36:37,380 --> 00:36:38,500
Mr. Yang told me

607
00:36:38,500 --> 00:36:40,020
that he would check the inbox every day.

608
00:36:40,380 --> 00:36:41,580
Who's Mr. Yang?

609
00:36:45,580 --> 00:36:46,380
Su Wei'an,

610
00:36:47,260 --> 00:36:48,700
if there's really a problem,

611
00:36:48,700 --> 00:36:49,820
just tell me.

612
00:36:49,900 --> 00:36:51,260
I can help you solve it together.

613
00:36:51,260 --> 00:36:52,220
No need.

614
00:36:52,420 --> 00:36:53,660
I can handle it myself.

615
00:36:54,380 --> 00:36:55,020
By the way,

616
00:36:55,380 --> 00:36:56,940
how many more files to translate?

617
00:36:57,220 --> 00:36:58,700
Can you give them to me in one go?

618
00:36:59,700 --> 00:37:01,460
I still need to take care of my aunt.

619
00:37:02,140 --> 00:37:04,140
I don't have that much time
to keep working for you.

620
00:37:04,420 --> 00:37:05,380
Still a lot to come.

621
00:37:06,020 --> 00:37:07,660
I'll tell you when I sort them out.

622
00:37:14,620 --> 00:37:15,220
Yuncheng?

623
00:37:19,980 --> 00:37:21,020
Yuncheng?

624
00:37:22,020 --> 00:37:23,780
Are you here to pick me up?

625
00:37:23,900 --> 00:37:24,660
Get in.

626
00:37:40,610 --> 00:37:42,260
It's windy at night.

627
00:37:43,140 --> 00:37:44,140
I'm so cold.

628
00:37:45,780 --> 00:37:47,620
Did you take Su Wei'an's report?

629
00:37:50,260 --> 00:37:52,180
You met me for Su Wei'an again?

630
00:37:52,620 --> 00:37:53,580
Just answer me

631
00:37:53,580 --> 00:37:54,660
yes or no.

632
00:37:55,260 --> 00:37:55,740
Yes.

633
00:37:56,660 --> 00:37:59,180
The Adverse Event Report she mailed

634
00:37:59,180 --> 00:38:00,140
was torn by me.

635
00:38:00,500 --> 00:38:01,140
What?

636
00:38:01,260 --> 00:38:03,300
She specially went to Jiehui to mail it?

637
00:38:03,500 --> 00:38:05,340
Or did you invite her
to a certain exhibition?

638
00:38:06,100 --> 00:38:07,020
I'm warning you.

639
00:38:07,780 --> 00:38:09,260
Stay away from Su Wei'an.

640
00:38:10,260 --> 00:38:11,860
Even if she's going
to ruin your project,

641
00:38:13,380 --> 00:38:15,300
you're still trying to defend her?

642
00:38:15,500 --> 00:38:16,860
That's between me and her.

643
00:38:17,020 --> 00:38:18,020
It has nothing to do with you.

644
00:38:18,660 --> 00:38:19,500
And,

645
00:38:20,300 --> 00:38:22,100
do not come to Jiehui anymore.

646
00:38:22,500 --> 00:38:23,980
We've broken up.

647
00:38:24,260 --> 00:38:26,780
Don't pretend
that you're still my girlfriend

648
00:38:26,780 --> 00:38:28,380
in front of my employees.

649
00:38:28,780 --> 00:38:29,780
If I run into that,

650
00:38:30,180 --> 00:38:31,660
don't blame me for being rude.

651
00:38:32,380 --> 00:38:33,260
I'm busy now.

652
00:38:33,780 --> 00:38:34,780
I can't drive you home.

653
00:38:36,380 --> 00:38:37,260
Yuncheng.

654
00:38:38,500 --> 00:38:39,500
Yuncheng!

655
00:38:55,780 --> 00:38:56,420
You're home.

656
00:38:56,860 --> 00:38:57,500
Mm.

657
00:39:07,500 --> 00:39:08,300
What happened?

658
00:39:09,100 --> 00:39:10,980
Did anyone bully my baby girl?

659
00:39:17,020 --> 00:39:17,980
What happened, Ran?

660
00:39:20,500 --> 00:39:21,140
Dad,

661
00:39:22,540 --> 00:39:24,020
am I a fool?

662
00:39:25,140 --> 00:39:26,780
Do I trust people too easily?

663
00:39:28,020 --> 00:39:29,260
What exactly is going on?

664
00:39:30,020 --> 00:39:30,780
Tell me.

665
00:39:32,180 --> 00:39:35,500
Do you still remember
my paper was wrongly accused,

666
00:39:35,500 --> 00:39:36,980
and my name was withdrawn from it?

667
00:39:38,620 --> 00:39:39,700
That classmate

668
00:39:39,900 --> 00:39:41,180
was called Su Wei'an.

669
00:39:41,660 --> 00:39:43,260
She was later expelled.

670
00:39:44,420 --> 00:39:46,140
A while ago, she approached me

671
00:39:46,900 --> 00:39:48,300
and asked me to help her aunt

672
00:39:48,300 --> 00:39:50,660
take part in the HDQ39 clinical trial.

673
00:39:52,260 --> 00:39:54,020
Haven't I told you already?

674
00:39:54,540 --> 00:39:56,260
That is a serious matter.

675
00:39:56,540 --> 00:39:58,260
The admission is all random.

676
00:39:58,500 --> 00:39:59,620
You can't interfere.

677
00:40:00,020 --> 00:40:01,140
Yeah.

678
00:40:01,500 --> 00:40:03,660
That's what I told her.

679
00:40:04,620 --> 00:40:06,260
But I don't know what has got into her.

680
00:40:07,100 --> 00:40:08,140
She has to spread rumors

681
00:40:08,140 --> 00:40:09,860
that HDQ39 has side effects.

682
00:40:10,860 --> 00:40:13,100
I think she's trying to get back at me.

683
00:40:14,020 --> 00:40:14,780
Ran,

684
00:40:15,380 --> 00:40:17,020
what exactly did she say?

685
00:40:17,500 --> 00:40:20,100
If there's truly an adverse event,

686
00:40:20,260 --> 00:40:21,860
I want to talk to her in person.

687
00:40:22,180 --> 00:40:23,300
No need, Dad.

688
00:40:24,380 --> 00:40:25,900
She's just dark-minded.

689
00:40:26,370 --> 00:40:27,540
She just hates to see me happy.

690
00:40:28,780 --> 00:40:30,100
You know what?

691
00:40:30,100 --> 00:40:31,610
Back at school,

692
00:40:32,140 --> 00:40:33,370
she had a crush on Yuncheng.

693
00:40:33,370 --> 00:40:35,660
Now she knows that I'm his girlfriend,

694
00:40:36,490 --> 00:40:38,100
she becomes jealous of me.

695
00:40:39,140 --> 00:40:41,020
Lately, she keeps badgering Yuncheng.

696
00:40:41,260 --> 00:40:42,300
Yuncheng ignores her,

697
00:40:42,980 --> 00:40:44,260
but she just won't give up.

698
00:40:44,860 --> 00:40:46,260
She just has to break us up.

699
00:40:46,740 --> 00:40:49,260
How can this girl be so shameless?

700
00:40:50,980 --> 00:40:52,180
Yeah.

701
00:40:54,380 --> 00:40:55,020
Dad,

702
00:40:56,020 --> 00:40:57,780
if she ever comes to bother you,

703
00:40:57,780 --> 00:40:59,620
you mustn't talk to her.

704
00:40:59,620 --> 00:41:00,420
I see.

705
00:41:00,980 --> 00:41:03,780
Alright, stop being upset now.

706
00:41:04,300 --> 00:41:06,180
Go take a shower and go to bed.

707
00:41:16,780 --> 00:41:18,140
Su Wei'an.

708
00:41:30,100 --> 00:41:31,020
Hi, Eliot.

709
00:41:31,380 --> 00:41:34,260
Gu, the literature and files
you asked me to look for,

710
00:41:34,260 --> 00:41:36,660
I've told my assistant
to send them to your mailbox.

711
00:41:37,380 --> 00:41:38,420
That's great, Eliot.

712
00:41:38,620 --> 00:41:39,420
Thank you.

713
00:41:39,900 --> 00:41:42,020
You did me a solid this time.

714
00:41:42,260 --> 00:41:44,140
What you told me to look for

715
00:41:44,140 --> 00:41:46,540
are the most cutting-edge
gene editing technologies.

716
00:41:46,980 --> 00:41:49,620
Will this help your research on gliomas?

717
00:41:49,620 --> 00:41:50,660
I have my reasons.

718
00:41:51,540 --> 00:41:52,380
How about this?

719
00:41:52,620 --> 00:41:55,020
I'll treat you to dinner
before you go back to your motherland.

720
00:41:55,260 --> 00:41:56,020
Bye.

