724
00:42:21,740 --> 00:42:24,500
When you finish them, your work is done.

725
00:42:33,980 --> 00:42:35,860
Where did you get
so much French literature?

726
00:42:37,100 --> 00:42:39,260
Take your time. I'm in no hurry.

727
00:42:40,180 --> 00:42:41,420
Be careful when you're translating.

728
00:42:41,740 --> 00:42:44,380
You'll have to redo it
if you mistranslate any.

729
00:42:44,540 --> 00:42:45,620
That'll be a huge waste of time.

730
00:42:46,380 --> 00:42:47,140
No worries.

731
00:42:47,300 --> 00:42:49,620
I'll definitely complete the mission
with due quality and quantity.

